#-        The Start§0
§0
§0Some say the war was§0
§0caused by NATO.§0
§0Others say Mir or§0
§0more specfically one§0
§0Mirian-Gregy165. §0
§0
§0While no one can come§0
§0to a conclusion§0
§0history will recognize§0
§0the victors as the§0
§0right. I however feel§0

#- it's important for§0

#- the people of§0
§0Civclassic to know both§0
§0sides. §0
§0
§0NATO at the time of the§0
§0soon to be war was§0
§0asked by one of it's§0
§0founding members§0
§0(HJE) to support and§0
§0assist HJEs efforts to§0
§0stop a griefer and§0
§0general nusiance in§0
§0HJEs lands coming§0

#- from MTA to there §0

#- south. This individual§0
§0was indentified as§0
§0Gregy165. NATO having§0
§0recently been formed§0
§0agreed but only in the§0
§0interest of protecting§0
§0there members. After§0
§0a few attempts to§0
§0pearl and drive him§0
§0out NATO seeked to§0
§0find a solution to rid§0
§0HJE from Gregy165.§0

#-       The Mirian§0
§0         Reason§0
§0
§0Gregy165 as mentioned§0
§0earlier was attacking§0
§0from or near MTA.§0
§0After countless§0
§0sorties and scrimishes§0
§0did NATO realize he§0
§0had a base of§0
§0operations in MTA.§0
