§0record attempted to§0

#- get Gregy165 to §0

#- leave and not come§0
§0back several times§0
§0peacefully. Sadly§0
§0because of those§0
§0events it lead NATO to§0
§0do something that while§0
§0it solved HJEs short§0
§0term problem would§0
§0cause bigger issues§0
§0down the line. A§0
§0coalition of NATO§0
§0members (mostly§0
§0combatants)§0

#- descended on§0

#- the location of§0
§0Gregy165s attack§0
§0bunker (Later to be§0
